022package com.restfb;
023
024import java.util.stream.Stream;
025
026public enum Version {
027
028  /**
029   * unversiond api
030   */
031  UNVERSIONED(null),
032
033  /**
034   * <tt>Graph API 9.0</tt>, available until February 23, 2023
035   *
036   * @since November 10th, 2020
037   */
038  VERSION_9_0("v9.0"),
039
040  /**
041   * <tt>Graph API 10.0</tt>, available until June 8th, 2023
042   *
043   * @since February 23th, 2021
044   */
045  VERSION_10_0("v10.0"),
046
047  /**
048   * <tt>Graph API 11.0</tt>, available until September 14th, 2023
049   *
050   * @since June 8th, 2021
051   */
052  VERSION_11_0("v11.0"),
053
054  /**
055   * <tt>Graph API 12.0</tt>, available until February 8th, 2024
056   *
057   * @since September 14th, 2021
058   */
059  VERSION_12_0("v12.0"),
060
061  /**
062   * <tt>Graph API 13.0</tt>, available until May 28th, 2024
063   *
064   * @since February 8th, 2022
065   */
066  VERSION_13_0("v13.0"),
067
068  /**
069   * <tt>Graph API 14.0</tt>, available until September 17th, 2024
070   *
071   * @since May 25th, 2022
072   */
073  VERSION_14_0("v14.0"),
074
075  /**
076   * <tt>Graph API 15.0</tt>, available at least until February 2nd, 2024
077   *
078   * @since September 17th, 2022
079   */
080  VERSION_15_0("v15.0"),
081
082  /**
083   * <tt>Graph API 16.0</tt>, available at least until February 2026
084   *
085   * @since February 2nd, 2023
086   */
087  VERSION_16_0("v16.0"),
088
089  /**
090   * convenience enum to provide simple access to the latest supported Graph API Version.
091   * <p>
092   * the current version is <tt>Graph API 14.0</tt>
093   * </p>
094   */
095  LATEST("v16.0");
096
097  private final String urlElement;
098
099  Version(String urlElement) {
100    this.urlElement = urlElement;
101  }
102
103  public String getUrlElement() {
104    return this.urlElement;
105  }
106
107  public boolean isUrlElementRequired() {
108    return null != this.urlElement;
109  }
110
111  /**
112   * converts a String (for example the url parameter) into a Version object
113   * 
114   * @param urlElementStr
115   *          String that should
116   * @return the generated version
117   */
118  public static Version getVersionFromString(String urlElementStr) {
119    if (urlElementStr != null) {
120      return Stream.of(Version.values()).filter(v -> urlElementStr.equals(v.getUrlElement())).findFirst()
121              .orElse(UNVERSIONED);
122    }
123
124    return UNVERSIONED;
125  }
126}
